name: Vol 1., Ch.7: The Climax
description: Tiara started screaming at the top of her lungs. It was not pain was she was experiencing, but just the opposite. Her vision became covered with a thousand color stars, and chills ran through her body. She could feel pleasure flowing throughout all her skin, and couldn’t help it but moan. Suddenly she felt how an explosion occurred, and her belly overflowed with beautiful sensations.
